This is not just enrichment.
This is Intelligent Document Processing (IDP) enrichment orchestration.

The API receives:

dealId

enrichmentType

metadata

documentName

accountNumber

documentType

legalEntity

etc

And returns enriched intelligence about that deal/document.

This is typical in:

Trade Finance

Loan Origination

Corporate Banking

KYC document processing

Now I will give you:

Clean enterprise request contract

Clean enterprise response contract

Error contract

Recommended metadata fields (real banking context)

Example input & output

No unnecessary generics.
Single reusable contract.
Production-grade structure.

1️⃣ REQUEST CONTRACT (Enterprise IDP Enrichment)
