  }
}

2️⃣ Why These Fields (Banking Context)
dealId

Primary business key.
Everything in banking is deal-centric.

documentName

Needed for:

Audit

Case reconstruction

Compliance

accountNumber

Used for:

Exposure checks

Risk aggregation

Sanctions screening

legalEntity

Important in global banks.
Routing depends on entity.

processingStage

Helps:

Underwriting

Credit decision

Compliance review

ocrConfidenceScore

IDP specific.
If confidence low → reprocess.

